PC Number: 2004-0266

Date: 2004-03-23

                 Whereas the Land O’Lakes Chamber of Commerce, in the Province of Ontario, the certificate of formation of which was recorded under the provisions of the Boards of Trade Act on December 12, 1990, has ceased to exercise its franchises;

 

                 Therefore, Her Excellency the Governor General in Council, on the recommendation of the Minister of Industry, pursuant to section 43 of the Boards of Trade Act, hereby dissolves as a corporation the Land O’Lakes Chamber of Commerce.


                 Attendu que la Land O’Lakes Chamber of Commerce (Ontario), dont le certificat de constitution a été enregistré en vertu de la Loi sur les chambres de commerce le 12 décembre 1990 a cessé d’exercer ses pouvoirs,

 

                 À ces causes, sur recommandation de la ministre de l’Industrie et en vertu de l’article 43 de la Loi sur les chambres de commerce, Son Excellence la Gouverneure générale en conseil dissout la Land O’Lakes Chamber of Commerce en tant que personne morale.
